content.rendered:
Hi everyone! It’s that time of year again! Happy HALLOWEEEEENIE!!

Of course, pumpkin themed everything is the favorite. So in that case, here are some PUMPKIN themed videos! A healthy pumpkin muffin recipe (had it last night!!), a pumpkin workout (wut?), and then how to make pumpkin seeds (soooo good for you).

They are all from last year and I just compiled them together! Happy Fall and ENJOY!

HEALTHY PUMPKIN MUFFIN RECIPE:

 

PUMPKIN WORKOUT: Total Body Workout Using Pumpkins as WEIGHTS! Ha!

 

How to make pumpkin seeds taste good, as they are so healthy for ya!!
